snippet.title: ViSP Mixed Reality Trailer - The Beginning
snippet.description:
Early Gameplay Teaser for our VR game ViSP. 
Construct a unique space station and defend it against enemies to create a flourishing space port! 
ViSP is currently in development for the HTC Vive.

For more information, check us out on:
http://www.virtualspaceport.com
http://twitter.com/ViSPgame 
http://fb.com/virtualspaceport

Music: Jaded Shadow by Jens Kiilstofte
